, Thou art Simon the son of Jona: thou shalt be called Cephas, which is by interpretation, A stone’ (John 1:42). According to Matthew 16:17–18, Christ says more explicitly, ‘Blessed art thou, Simon Bar-jona … thou art Peter, and upon this rock I will build my church’. The name has been in continuous use since the Middle Ages."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Peter Legh was born in 1275. He had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1275–":"1275–Surnud","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295"},"fi":{"1275–":"1275–Kuollut","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295"},"fr":{"1275–":"1275–Décédé","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","lifeSummary":"Peter Legh est né en 1275. Il a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1275–":"1275–Verstorben","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Verstorben","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","lifeSummary":"Peter Legh wurde 1275 geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1275–":"1275–Desede","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Desede","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295"},"hu":{"1275–":"1275–elhunyt","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–elhunyt","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295"},"id":{"1275–":"1275–Telah Meninggal","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Telah Meninggal","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295"},"it":{"1275–":"1275–Deceduto","1295–1355":"1295–1355","1275–Male":"1275–Deceduto","1355":"1355","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","lifeSummary":"Peter Legh è nato il nel 1275. Lui avuto almeno 1 figlia."},"ja":{"1275–":"1275年–死亡","1295–1355":"1295年–1355年","1275–Male":"1275年–死亡","1355":"1355年","1275":"1275年","1295":"1295年","lifeSummary":"Peter Leghは1275年に生まれた。彼は少なくとも1人の娘をもうけた。"},"ko":{"1275–":"1275년–사망","1295–1355":"1295년–1355년","1275–Male":"1275년–사망","1355":"1355년","1275":"1275년","1295":"1295년","lifeSummary":"Peter Legh(은)는 1275년 태어났다. 그는 적어도 한 명의 딸을 두었다."